781
01:25:37,240 --> 01:25:39,800
You're not a goblin's bride.

782
01:25:46,470 --> 01:25:48,470
Wait.

783
01:25:51,890 --> 01:25:54,660
I'm not done talking.

784
01:26:02,680 --> 01:26:07,030
