785
01:26:07,030 --> 01:26:10,300
You! How did you get here?

786
01:26:12,020 --> 01:26:14,730
Grab the handle and push.

787
01:26:14,730 --> 01:26:17,020
Follow you.

788
01:26:17,820 --> 01:26:19,270
